","workspace_file_chunks":[]},{"status":"success","request_id":"fa766c07-7a21-4712-bb2f-70a4d32ccd6b","request_message":"","structured_output_nodes":[{"id":1,"type":0,"content":"The integration is now complete! The key functionality is in the `PortalRTPTask` where it filters out players in combat before teleportation occurs. Players who are in combat will:

