### ⚙️ **Configuration Options:**

````yaml path=src/main/resources/config.yml mode=EXCERPT
# Water/Liquid detection settings to prevent teleporting into dangerous areas
water-detection:
 # Whether to prevent teleporting into areas with too much water/lava
